window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Her father stole the source of all magic. Now she will be beheadedâ€¦</b></p> <p>In a realm starved of magic, Vellene Winloc is next in line to inherit it, but her abusive, tyrannical father will never let her have it.</p> <p>Surrounded by the heads of her father's conquests, she must defy years of physical and emotional abuse if she ever wants to give the rage within her a voice.</p> <p>Out of his mind on drugs, Eledar Lirik is one of the last of the golem in the realm. After leading his species to their deaths, he traded heroism for drowning.</p> <p>That is until the mysterious, masked leader of a resistance group offers him a chance to steal the source of all magic.</p> <p>She's voiceless. He's desperate. But he will betray her.</p> <p>And she will burn them all.</p> <p><i>Welcome to the realm of Alchemight where the consequences of power are ten-fold. </i>For Mist and Tar <i>and</i> For Blood and Flame <i>complete a grimdark, tragic, romantic fantasy duology between a furious heiress, a scarred enemy, a haunted hero, and a girl rotted by death.</i></p> <p><i>For fans of One Dark Window meets Mistborn. Completed Grimdark Epic Romantic Fantasy Duology. A tragic love story and the end of an entire realm.</i></p> <p><i>Contains mature content. A complete list of content warnings can be found on the author's website.</i></p>"; 
